files.patch:
@@ -78,17 +78,17 @@ sendmsg.o: sendmsg.c fflags
 	$(GCC_FOR_TARGET) `cat fflags` -c $(GCC_CFLAGS) $(SUBDIR_INCLUDES) $(srcdir)/objc/sendmsg.c
 
 ## Next to are for heuristics on forwarding mechanism... 
-_forward: _forward.c
-	-$(GCC_FOR_TARGET) -c $(GCC_CFLAGS) $(SUBDIR_INCLUDES) $(srcdir)/objc/_forward.c
-	-$(GCC_FOR_TARGET) ./_forward.o -o _forward
-	if [ ! -f ./_forward ]; then touch ./_forward; fi	
+xforward: xforward.c
+	-$(GCC_FOR_TARGET) -c $(GCC_CFLAGS) $(SUBDIR_INCLUDES) $(srcdir)/objc/xforward.c
+	-$(GCC_FOR_TARGET) ./xforward.o -o xforward
+	if [ ! -f ./xforward ]; then touch ./xforward; fi	
 
-fflags: _forward
+fflags: xforward
 	-rm -f fflags
-	-if [ -s ./_forward ]; then ./_forward > fflags; else touch fflags; fi
+	-if [ -s ./xforward ]; then ./xforward > fflags; else touch fflags; fi
 
 mostlyclean:
-	-rm -f *.o libobjc.a _forward fflags
+	-rm -f *.o libobjc.a xforward fflags
 clean: mostlyclean
 distclean: mostlyclean
 extraclean: mostlyclean
